---
// Features.astro - Display the key features of Bomfather
---

<section class="py-16 bg-light-gray">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold font-heading mb-4">Key Features</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-mid-gray max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Bomfather offers unique capabilities to secure your software supply chain through kernel-level monitoring and verification.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Feature 1 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Kernel-Level Monitoring</h3>
        <p class="text-mid-gray">
          Track dependencies directly at the kernel level using eBPF, ensuring complete visibility of all files accessed during builds.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Feature 2 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Tamper-Evident Verification</h3>
        <p class="text-mid-gray">
          Verify the integrity of your software supply chain with cryptographic Merkle trees that provide tamper-evident proof of build provenance.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Feature 3 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 7v10c0 2.21 3.582 4 8 4s8-1.79 8-4V7M4 7c0 2.21 3.582 4 8 4s8-1.79 8-4M4 7c0-2.21 3.582-4 8-4s8 1.79 8 4m0 5c0 2.21-3.582 4-8 4s-8-1.79-8-4" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Accurate SBOMs</h3>
        <p class="text-mid-gray">
          Generate comprehensive Software Bills of Materials (SBOMs) that include dynamically loaded and conditional dependencies often missed by other tools.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Feature 4 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">High Performance</h3>
        <p class="text-mid-gray">
          Optimized eBPF-based implementation with minimal overhead during build processes, ensuring performance isn't compromised.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Feature 5 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11 4a2 2 0 114 0v1a1 1 0 001 1h3a1 1 0 011 1v3a1 1 0 01-1 1h-1a2 2 0 100 4h1a1 1 0 011 1v3a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3a1 1 0 01-1-1v-1a2 2 0 10-4 0v1a1 1 0 01-1 1H7a1 1 0 01-1-1v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H4a2 2 0 110-4h1a1 1 0 001-1V7a1 1 0 011-1h3a1 1 0 001-1V4z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Integration Ready</h3>
        <p class="text-mid-gray">
          Seamlessly integrate with existing CI/CD pipelines, build systems, and security tools for automated dependency verification.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Feature 6 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6V4m0 2a2 2 0 100 4m0-4a2 2 0 110 4m-6 8a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 110-4m0 4v2m0-6V4m6 6v10m6-2a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 110-4m0 4v2m0-6V4" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Customizable</h3>
        <p class="text-mid-gray">
          Flexible configuration options to adapt to your specific project requirements, build environments, and security policies.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 